    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can have your list sorted in a very simple way, by inserting each item in the correct position when you add them to the list. </p>\n\n<pre><code>public void sortedInsert(Item item){\n    for ( int i = 0; i&lt; yourList.size(); i++) {\n        if ( item.getDistance() &lt; yourList.get(i).getDistance()){\n            yourList.add(i, item);\n            return;\n         }\n    }\n    // If the item hasn't been inserted\n    yourList.add(item);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
