    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Make sure  <code>o1.getDistance()</code> return <code>Double</code>, if not , use <code>Double.parse(o1.getDistance())</code> for <code>o1</code> and <code>o2</code>.</p>\n"
